{"tid":2184812,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"湯家驊：是否三權分立爭拗無謂","createTime":"2020-09-02T00:38:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T05:24:14.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b7499abaa86f7fa25b360acbbe397da37613bb94","tid":2184812,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T00:38:14.000Z","msg":"行政會議成員、資深大律師湯家驊指，本港有無「三權分立」的爭拗有點無謂。<br />\n<br />\n他解釋，在基本法下，本港內部治權的政治概念上，有某程度分隔和互相制衡，但憲制安排上沒有三權分立。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊在一個電台節目上指，本港不會因為行政長官林鄭月娥說沒有三權分立，而一夜間失去權力分隔；也不會因為法律界議員郭榮鏗說有三權分立，而改變憲制秩序，認為爭拗無謂。<br />\n<br />\n他指，本港有三權分工，亦有互相制衡，而回歸以來權力亦能達至互相制衡的效果。 湯家驊相信，現時本港處於獨立思想醞釀的敏感時刻，中央政府認為討論獨立政體的「三權分立」並不恰當。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2355292\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2355292&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=f156a3f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2355292</a>"},{"pid":"8fa2279101c8def6ecf4f5c88f0deb1e23a576be","tid":2184812,"uid":125380,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T00:42:21.000Z","msg":"是否未成年爭拗無謂"},{"pid":"e959846e7f35ecb94f8a4df9aa102ce630f5ff5e","tid":2184812,"uid":313764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8fa2279101c8def6ecf4f5c88f0deb1e23a576be","tid":2184812,"uid":125380,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T00:42:21.000Z","msg":"是否未成年爭拗無謂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T00:43:04.000Z","msg":"屌比你早過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c6bb8be5c18977744a78aea3522aa9ff7243d3","tid":2184812,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T00:43:42.000Z","msg":"你話無謂就無謂，好大個官威"},{"pid":"9a1b60587d46a2244cf8466f8acea321e35e3fd3","tid":2184812,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T00:46:16.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span